name: Cuadro #3
description:
This image is based on the famous painting known as Starry Night (1889) by Vincent Van Gogh.

Cuadro #3 is part of a collection.

It was generated algorithmically with Python and Pillow. 60,300 pixels were randomly taken that are reflected as a rectangle of the same color as its corresponding pixel with a certain random level of transparency. The size of the rectangle is also random up to a maximum of 160. The location of the rectangle does not exactly match its pixel, but is slightly randomly misplaced.

Previous pieces in this collection: OBJKT#452088 and OBJKT#458131

Size: 5548 x 4496 px.
